data.description: Comfortable mountain contemporary.  Views of Mount Rosalie,  Easy commute with quick access back to 285. Main floor has beautiful wood floors with custom inlays.  Large lower room that could be Primary suite with it's own bath or a second living area. Was previously used as a lock off rental..  Enjoy the large deck for all your entertaining.  The kitchen has room for a dining table.  Wood burning stove in the main living room.
